These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-2-1::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: d&b, country, funk, pop
1. the fan of country is between the fan of funk and the fan of pop##2
2. the fan of country is on the left of the fan of funk##1
3. the fan of d&b is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |  2   |  3   |   4   |
| Music-Genre   | d&b | pop | country | funk |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-2-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, sprite, water, juice
1. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
2. the person drinking water is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
3. the person drinking juice is between the person drinking sprite and the person drinking 7up##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |  3   |    4     |
| Beverage   | sprite | juice | 7up | water |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-2-3::.
4 different pets are kept: hamster, goat, fish, frog
1. the owner of the frog is on the right of the owner of the hamster##1
2. the owner of the fish is between the owner of the goat and the owner of the frog##2
3. the owner of the hamster is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |  1   |   2    |  3   |   4    |
| Pet   | hamster | frog | fish | goat |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-2-4::.
